  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the clams under cold water and pat them dry with a paper towel.",
    "Heat the ghee in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the clams, olive oil, lemon juice, salt, and black pepper to the skillet.",
    "Cover the skillet and cook for 3-5 minutes, until the clams open.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and cooked fold.",
    "Serve the clams and fold hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
